{
  "doc_id": "42629",
  "text": "Six to eight week old female 129/Sv6C57BL/6 mice were purchased from Harlan UK Ltd. (Oxfordshire, UK). Prnp 0/0 mice used here were derived from the original Zurich I mice [CITATION_1] and crossed onto the FVB/N background for 10 generations [CITATION_2] . Mice were inoculated intraperitoneally (i.p.) with 100 ml of 1% Rocky Mountain Laboratory (RML) prion strain I6200 [CITATION_3] or 1% uninfected CD1 brain homogenate and culled at early stages of prion disease prior to the manifestation of neurological symptoms.",
